        "episode_id": "ac5784fa-1c94-5cd8-99c6-c4f0be157a64",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Welcome back to Long Horizon Notes. Today we're talking about index investing, and I'm joined by Daniel Cho, former bond trader turned index advocate. Daniel Cho, thanks for being here.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 6000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 0,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p05_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "person:speaker-02",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Daniel Cho"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:7f22144da157055b",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 301,
        "char_start": 204,
        "episode_id": "ac5784fa-1c94-5cd8-99c6-c4f0be157a64",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Thanks, Nora. Excited for this one \u2014 index investing is something I've been thinking about a lot.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 12000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 6000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p05_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:54d9a201259a2e7d",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 429,
        "char_start": 308,
        "episode_id": "ac5784fa-1c94-5cd8-99c6-c4f0be157a64",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "This episode is brought to you by Vanguard. Vanguard pioneered low-cost index funds. Get started at vanguard.com/podcast.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 18000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 12000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p05_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:d33dfc8aae77fbed",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 507,
        "char_start": 429,
        "episode_id": "ac5784fa-1c94-5cd8-99c6-c4f0be157a64",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "What does the failure mode look like? How does Vanguard fit into this picture?",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 24000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 18000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p05_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:addf65b8736872c1",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 736,
        "char_start": 520,
        "episode_id": "ac5784fa-1c94-5cd8-99c6-c4f0be157a64",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Let me give you the version I actually believe. Index funds are not a strategy \u2014 they're the absence of one. We've seen this play out at teams using Vanguard. And the second-order effect is the part most people miss.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 30000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 24000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p05_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
